  <script type="text/javascript">
   function CloseMobileMenu() {
        $("#Container_Main").animate({ left: "0" }, {
            complete: function () {
                $("#Mobile_MegaNav").removeClass("mainMenuOpen");
                $(this).removeClass("mainMenuOpen");

                // Close any open sub menus
                $("#Mobile_MegaNav .openDiv").slideUp(0, function () {
                    $(this).removeClass("openDiv").addClass("hideDiv");
                });

                // Reset the containers positioning with the preserved value
                var scrollVal = $(this).css("top");
                $(this).css({ top: 0 });
                window.scrollTo(0, -parseInt(scrollVal));
            }
        });
    }

    function OpenMobileMenu() {
        var nav = $("#Mobile_MegaNav");
        var scrollVal = $(document).scrollTop();

        $("#Container_Main").addClass("mainMenuOpen").animate({ left: nav.outerWidth() }).css({ top: -scrollVal });
        nav.addClass("mainMenuOpen");
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        var touchStartX;
        var touchDirection = undefined;
        var touchThreshhold = 100;
        direction = {
            up: "up",
            right: "right",
            down: "down",
            left: "left"
        }

        // Click function for the mobile "Menu" icon
        $("#Mobile_MegaNav_Icon").click(function () {
            if ($("#Container_Main").css("left") === $("#Mobile_MegaNav").css("width")) {
                CloseMobileMenu();
            }
            else {
                OpenMobileMenu();
            }
        });

        // Click function for the "Hide Menu" link inside of the mobile meun
        $("#Mobile_MegaNav_HideMenu").click(function () {
            CloseMobileMenu();
        });

        // Disable the main site when the mobile menu is open
        $("#Container_Main").click(function (e) {
            if ($("#Container_Main").css("left") === $("#Mobile_MegaNav").css("width")) {
                CloseMobileMenu();
                e.preventDefault();
                e.stopPropagation();

                return false;
            }
        });

        //mobile meganav accordion list
        $("#Mobile_MegaNav_Categories &gt; li").each(function () {
            var acco_Content = $(this).children("ul");

            $(this).children("span").click(function () {
                if (acco_Content.hasClass("hideDiv")) {
                    $("#Mobile_MegaNav .openDiv").slideUp("normal", function () {
                        $(this).removeClass("openDiv").addClass("hideDiv");
                    });
                    acco_Content.slideDown("normal", function () {
                        acco_Content.addClass("openDiv").removeClass("hideDiv");
                    });
                }
                else {
                    acco_Content.slideUp("normal", function () {
                        acco_Content.removeClass("openDiv").addClass("hideDiv");
                    });
                }
            }); // End header click listener
        }); // End each loop

        // Touch Start Event
        function HandleTouchStart(evt) {
            var touches = evt.changedTouches;
            touchStartX = (touches.length &gt;= 0) ? touches[0].pageX : undefined;
            touchDirection = undefined;
        }


        // Touch Move Event
        function HandleTouchDrag(evt) {
            var touches = evt.changedTouches;
            touchDirection = (touches.length === 0 || Math.abs(touches[0].pageX - touchStartX) &lt;= touchThreshhold) ? undefined
                : (touches[0].pageX &gt;= touchStartX) ? direction.right
                : direction.left;
        }


        // Touch End Event
        function HandleTouchEnd(evt) {
            switch (touchDirection) {
                case direction.right:
                    {
                        OpenMobileMenu();
                        break;
                    }
                case direction.left:
                    {
                        CloseMobileMenu();
                        break;
                    }
            }
        }
        if (GetRFCookie('IsDesktopMode') != 'true') {
            if (window.addEventListener) {
                window.addEventListener("touchstart", HandleTouchStart, false);
                window.addEventListener("touchmove", HandleTouchDrag, false);
                window.addEventListener("touchend", HandleTouchEnd, false);
                // Touch Cancel Events
                window.addEventListener("touchcancel", HandleTouchEnd, false);
                window.addEventListener("touchleave", HandleTouchEnd, false);
            } else if (window.attachEvent) {
                window.attachEvent("touchstart", HandleTouchStart, false);
                window.attachEvent("touchmove", HandleTouchDrag, false);
                window.attachEvent("touchend", HandleTouchEnd, false);
                // Touch Cancel Events
                window.attachEvent("touchcancel", HandleTouchEnd, false);
                window.attachEvent("touchleave", HandleTouchEnd, false);
            }
        }
    }); //End document.ready

    $(window).resize(function () {
        if ($(window).width() &gt;= 667 &amp;&amp; $("#Container_Main").hasClass("mainMenuOpen")) {
            CloseMobileMenu();
        }
    }); //End window.resize
  </script>

           // Add trim function to String class to use in trimming keywords.
    String.prototype.trim = function () {
        return this.replace(/^\s*/, "").replace(/\s*$/, "");
       }

    function OnClientPopulated(sender, e) {
        var ace = $find("aceSearchSuggestions");

        if (ace &amp;&amp; ace._currentPrefix) {
            var list = ace.get_completionList();
            var prefix = ace._currentPrefix.trim().toLowerCase();

            // Process Search Suggestions
            for (var i = 0; i &lt; list.childNodes.length; i++) {
                // Parse Data
                var data = list.childNodes[i]._value.trim().split(":@:");
                var name = (data.length &gt; 0) ? data[0] : null;
                var imgURL = (data.length &gt; 1) ? data[1] : null;
                var url = (data.length &gt; 2) ? data[2] : null;

                // Build Markup
                var innerHTML = "&lt;div class='autocomplete-item'&gt;";

                // Build Image
                if (imgURL) {
                    var img = "&lt;div class='autocomplete-item-img'&gt;";
                    img += "&lt;img src='" + imgURL + "' alt='' /&gt;";
                    img += "&lt;/div&gt;";
                    innerHTML += img;
                }

                // Build Text
                var txt = "&lt;div class='autocomplete-item-text'&gt;";
                txt += name.replace(new RegExp(prefix, 'gi'), "&lt;span class='heavyText'&gt;" + prefix + "&lt;/span&gt;");
                txt += "&lt;/div&gt;";
                innerHTML += txt;

                // Handle Name
                innerHTML += "&lt;input type='hidden' class='acItemName' value='" + name + "' /&gt;";

                // Handle Redirect URL
                if (url) {
                    innerHTML += "&lt;input type='hidden' class='acItemRedirect' value='" + url + "' /&gt;";
                }

                innerHTML += "&lt;/div&gt;";

                // Set Markup
                list.childNodes[i].innerHTML = innerHTML;
            }
        }
    }

    function OnClientItemSelected(sender, e) {
        var container = ($(e._item).hasClass("autocomplete_listItem") || $(e._item).hasClass("autocomplete_highlightedListItem"))
            ? $(e._item)
            : $(e._item).parents(".autocomplete_listItem, .autocomplete_highlightedListItem");
        var name = container.find(".acItemName").val();
        var url = container.find(".acItemRedirect").val();
        
        if (url &amp;&amp; url != '') {
            $("#ctl00_ctl00_Header1_uxGEO_uxViewQuickSearch_txtKeyword").val(name);
            window.location = url;
        } else {
            sender.get_element().value = name;
            $get("ctl00_ctl00_Header1_uxGEO_uxViewQuickSearch_btnSearch").click();
        }
    }

      <script type="text/javascript">
       $().rf_initTurnTo("JTSqWITZSLEj1v7site");

    function ProductEndRequestHandler() {
        $('div.Product_AccordionHeader').off("click");
        SetAccordian();
        var accordionID = $("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_uxProduct_hfActiveAccordion").val();
        if (accordionID !== undefined) {
            var accordionHeader = document.getElementById(accordionID);
            if (accordionHeader) {
                var accordionContent = $(accordionHeader).next();
                $(accordionHeader).addClass('Product_AccordionOpen');
                $(accordionContent).addClass('openDiv')               
                $(accordionContent).slideDown(0, function () {
                    if (!$(accordionHeader).isOnScreen()) {
                        $('html, body').animate({
                            scrollTop: $(accordionHeader).offset().top
                        }, 600);
                    }
                });
             }
        }
        RF_ResetTurnTo("RF_MarkTurnToReviews");
        RF_ResetTurnTo("RF_MarkTurnToQuestions");
        $().rf_initTurnTo("JTSqWITZSLEj1v7site");
    }

    function SetAccordian() {
        //ACCORDION BUTTON ACTION
        $('div.Product_AccordionHeader').click(function () {
            var accordionHeader = $(this);
            var accordionContent = $(this).next();
            //if (Product_AccordionContent.hasClass('Product_AccordionContent')) {
            //IF THE DIV YOU CLICKED IS ALREADY OPEN, CLOSE AND REMOVE THE OPEN CLASS
            if (accordionContent.hasClass('openDiv')) {
                accordionContent.slideUp('normal', function () {
                    accordionHeader.removeClass('Product_AccordionOpen');
                    accordionContent.removeClass('openDiv');
                    accordionContent.attr('style', '');
                });
                $("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_uxProduct_hfActiveAccordion").val("");
            }
            //CLOSE ANY OPEN DIVS, OPEN THE CLICKED DIV
            else {
                $('div.Product_AccordionHeader').removeClass('Product_AccordionOpen');
                $('div.Product_AccordionContent.openDiv').slideUp('normal', function () {
                    $(this).removeClass('openDiv');
                });
                accordionHeader.addClass('Product_AccordionOpen');
                accordionContent.slideDown('normal', function () {
                    if (!accordionHeader.isOnScreen()) {
                        $('html, body').animate({
                            scrollTop: $(accordionHeader).offset().top
                        }, 600);
                    }
                }).addClass('openDiv');
                $("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_uxProduct_hfActiveAccordion").val($(accordionHeader).attr("id"));
            }
            $.fn.isOnScreen = function () {
                var win = $(window);
                var viewport = {
                    top: win.scrollTop(),
                    left: win.scrollLeft()
                };
                viewport.right = viewport.left + win.width();
                viewport.bottom = viewport.top + win.height();

                var bounds = this.offset();
                bounds.right = bounds.left + this.outerWidth();
                bounds.bottom = bounds.top + this.outerHeight();

                return (!(viewport.right &lt; bounds.left || viewport.left &gt; bounds.right || viewport.bottom &lt; bounds.top || viewport.top &gt; bounds.bottom));
            };
        });       // End Product Accordion

        $('.Product_Accordion').each(function () {
            $(this).children('.Product_AccordionHeader').last().addClass('Product_AccordionFooter');
        });
        
        // qTip for Swatches
        //var adjustY = 0;
        $('.SmallSwatch, .SmallCustomSwatch').each(function () {
            $(this).qtip({
                content: { text: $(this).next('div') },
                style: { classes: 'qtip-bootstrap .qtip-ClickThrough', tip: { corner: false} },
                //position: { effect: false, my: 'bottom center', at: 'top center', target: $(this), adjust: { x:0, y: adjustY } },
                position: { effect: false, my: 'bottom center', at: 'top center', target: $(this) },
                hide: { fixed: true }
            });
        });

        // Responsive Tooltips
        EnableQtips();
        $( window ).resize(function() { EnableQtips(); });
    }

    function OpenReviews()
    {
        if(!$('#divReviews').next().hasClass('openDiv'))
        {
            $('#divReviews').trigger("click");                
        }
        var x = $('#divReviews').offset().top - 50; 
        $('html,body').animate({ scrollTop: x }, 500);
    }

    function getParameterByName(name) {
        name = name.replace(/[\[]/, "\\[").replace(/[\]]/, "\\]");
        var regex = new RegExp("[\\?&amp;]" + name + "=([^&amp;#]*)"),
        results = regex.exec(location.search);
        return results == null ? "" : decodeURIComponent(results[1].replace(/\+/g, " "));
    }
    
    function EnableQtips()
    {
        var disabled = ($(window).width() &lt;= 640) ? true : false;
        $('.SmallSwatch').each(function () {
            $(this).qtip('api').disable(disabled);
        });
    }

    $(window).load(function () {
        // Show Reviews on Load
        if (getParameterByName('readrev') == "true") {
            OpenReviews();
        } else if (getParameterByName('writerev') == "true") {
            OpenReviews();
            TurnTo.writeReview();
        }
    });

    $(document).ready(function () {
        SetAccordian();
    });

    Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(ProductEndRequestHandler);
      </script>

        <script type="text/javascript">
         function Init_Viewer() {
        var viewer = document.getElementById("product_viewer");
        if (viewer &amp;&amp; viewer.childNodes.length != 0) return;

        // Fn to generate Random string with the Scene 7 format
        function genInstance() {
            var curDateTime = new Date();
            var curTime = "ZoomMX" + curDateTime.getHours() + curDateTime.getMinutes() + curDateTime.getSeconds();
            return curTime;
        }

        function embedFlyout() {
            var flyoutViewer = new s7viewers.FlyoutViewer({
                "containerId": "product_viewer",
                "params": {
                    asset: assetPath,
                    serverurl: "http://raymourflanigan.scene7.com/is/image/",
                    contenturl: "http://raymourflanigan.scene7.com/skins/",
                    config: "RaymourandFlanigan/ProductPage_FlyOut"
                }
            }).init();
        }

        function embedZoomViewer() {
            var zoomViewer = new s7viewers.ZoomViewer({
                "containerId": "product_viewer",
                "params": {
                    "asset": assetPath,
                    "serverurl": "http://raymourflanigan.scene7.com/is/image/"
                }
            }).init();
        }

        /* * * PRODUCT IMAGE MAIN * * */
        // If not just loading a static image, we need to decide which viewer to use.
        var s7url = document.getElementById('ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_uxProduct_uxProductImageViewer_hfS7url').value;
        var assetPath = "RaymourandFlanigan/" + s7url;
        if (s7url != '') {
            var browser = s7ueUtils.browser.getName();
            var version = s7ueUtils.browser.getVersion();
            var deviceName = s7ueUtils.device.getName();
            // Detect Internet Explorer 8: Use the Flash Viewer. Responsive jQuery viewer proved too problematic on the old browser.
            if (deviceName == "desktop" &amp;&amp; browser == "IE" &amp;&amp; (version == 8 || version == 7)) {
                // S7 Vars for Flash
                var myName = genInstance();
                var isViewerRoot = "http://s7d5.scene7.com/is-viewers/";
                var viewerType = "genericzoom";
                var isRoot = "http://s7d5.scene7.com/is/image/";
                var skinsRoot = "http://s7d5.scene7.com/skins/";
                // Use a smaller viewer when inside of a popup
                var configName = "RaymourandFlanigan/FlashZoom_ProductDetail";
                
                // Build Flash Viewer Path
                var viewerUrl = "";
                viewerUrl += isViewerRoot;
                viewerUrl += "flash/" + viewerType + ".swf?";
                viewerUrl += "serverUrl=" + isRoot;
                viewerUrl += "&amp;contentRoot=" + skinsRoot;
                viewerUrl += "&amp;instanceName=" + myName;
                viewerUrl += "&amp;image=" + assetPath;
                viewerUrl += "&amp;config=" + configName;

                // flashvars tag elements
                var flashvars = {};

                // param tag elements
                var params = {
                    allowScriptAccess: "Always",
                    menu: "false",
                    quality: "high",
                    scale: "noscale",
                    salign: "LT",
                    bgcolor: "#FFFFFF",
                    wmode: "transparent"
                };

                // object tag elements
                var attributes = {
                    id: myName,
                    name: myName
                };

                // Embed viewer on the page
                swfobject.embedSWF(viewerUrl, "product_viewer", "500", "420", "6.0.65.0", null, flashvars, params, attributes, null);
            } else if (deviceName == "desktop") {
                // Load the desktop responsive viewer
                embedFlyout();
            } else {
                // Load the mobile responsive viewer
                embedZoomViewer();
            }
        }
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        Init_Viewer();
        Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(Init_Viewer);
    });
        </script>

            <script type="text/javascript">
             // Partial Post-back handling
    function ProductBulletEndRequest(sender, args) {
        if (args.get_error() == undefined) {
            AdjustBullets();
            SetBulletHover();
        }
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        AdjustBullets();
        SetBulletHover();

        if (!window.attachEvent) {
            window.addEventListener("resize", AdjustBullets);
        }

        Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(ProductBulletEndRequest);
    });

    var adjustBulletsTimeout;
    function AdjustBullets() {
        // No bullets on the page
        if (!$(".ProductBulletContainer").length) {
            return;
        }

        // If the bullets haven't been rendered on the page due to being in a modal popup, wait and try again
        var hasWidth = $(".ProductBulletContainer").first().parent().width();
        if (!hasWidth) {
            if (!!adjustBulletsTimeout) { clearTimeout(adjustBulletsTimeout); }
            adjustBulletsTimeout = setTimeout(function () {
                AdjustBullets();
            }, 100);

            return;
        }

        if ($(window).innerWidth() &gt; 667) {
            $(".ProductBulletContainer").each(function (index, bullet) {
                var bulletContainer = $(bullet).parent();
                var tooltip = $(bullet).children().next();
                var offsetX = $(bullet).offset().left - $(bulletContainer).offset().left;

                $(tooltip).css("left", offsetX * -1);
                $(tooltip).css("width", $(bulletContainer).css("width"));
            });
        }
        else {
            $(".ProductBulletContainer").each(function (index, bullet) {
                var bulletContainer = $(bullet).parent();
                var tooltip = $(bullet).children().next();

                $(tooltip).css("left", 0);
                $(tooltip).css("width", "100%");
            });
        }
    }

    function SetBulletHover() {
        $('.ProductTooltip').mouseenter(function () {
            $(this).prev().addClass('ProductTooltipHover')
        }).mouseleave(function () {
            $(this).prev().removeClass('ProductTooltipHover')
        });
        $('.ProductFreeShipping').mouseenter(function () {
            $(this).prev().addClass('ProductFreeShippingHover')
        }).mouseleave(function () {
            $(this).prev().removeClass('ProductFreeShippingHover')
        });
    }
            </script>

         <script type="text/javascript">
          function OpenReviewsDiv() {
        var header = $('#divReviews');

        if (!header.hasClass('Product_AccordionOpen')) {
            header.click();
        }
        var x = $('#divReviews').offset().top - 100;
        $('html,body').animate({ scrollTop: x }, 500);
    }

    function OpenQADiv() {
        var header = $('#divQA');

        if (!header.hasClass('Product_AccordionOpen')) {
            header.click();
        }
        var x = $('#divQA').offset().top - 100;
        $('html,body').animate({ scrollTop: x }, 500);
    }

    function AskQuestion() {
        OpenQADiv();
    }

    function WriteReview() {
        OpenReviewsDiv();
        TurnTo.writeReview();
    }

    function SetReviewsText() {
        var Questions = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_uxProduct_uxProductInformation_lblQuestionCount");
        var Answers = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_uxProduct_uxProductInformation_lblAnswerCount");
        var lnkQA = document.getElementById("lnkQA");
        var QuestionCount = ("TurnToItemData" in window) ? TurnToItemData.counts.q : 0;
        var AnswerCount = ("TurnToItemData" in window) ? TurnToItemData.counts.a : 0;

        // Check for questions
        if (QuestionCount &gt; 0) {
            Questions.innerHTML = (QuestionCount != '1') ? 'See ' + QuestionCount + ' Questions' : 'See 1 Question';

            if (AnswerCount &gt; 0) {
                Answers.innerHTML = (AnswerCount != '1') ? ':: ' + AnswerCount + ' Answers' : ':: 1 Answer';
            }
            else {
                $('#lblAnswerCount').css("display", "none");
            }
        }
        else {
            $('#lnkQA').css("display", "none");
        }
    }

    function SetTurnToSku() {
        TurnToItemSku = $('#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_uxProduct_uxProductInformation_hfTurnToSku').val();
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        SetTurnToSku();
        SetReviewsText();
        $.getScript("http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js");
    });

    Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(SetReviewsText);
    Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(SetTurnToSku);
    Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(SocialMediaEndRequest);

    function SocialMediaEndRequest(sender, args) {
        $.getScript("http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js");
    }
         </script>

and the date of your claim.

date we agree to replace your furniture.

        //getCookie
        function GetCookie(name, key) {
            var value = '';

            if (name &amp;&amp; name.trim() != '') {
                name = name.trim();
                // Check Cookies
                var cookies = document.cookie.split(';');
                for (var i = 0; i &lt; cookies.length; i++) {
                    var cookie = cookies[i].trim();
                    if (cookie.toLowerCase().indexOf(name.toLowerCase()) == 0) {
                        // Grab Cookie Value
                        value = cookie.substring(name.length + 1, cookie.length);
                        break;
                    }
                }

                if (key &amp;&amp; key.trim() != '') {
                    key = key.trim();
                    // Check Embedded Keys
                    var keypairs = value.split('&amp;');
                    for (var x = 0; x &lt; keypairs.length; x++) {
                        var keypair = keypairs[x].trim();
                        if (keypair.toLowerCase().indexOf(key.toLowerCase()) == 0) {
                            // Grab Key Value
                            value = keypair.substring(key.length + 1, keypair.length);
                            break;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            return value;
        }

        //set Cookies
        function SetCookie(Name, Value, Expiration) {
            
            var d = new Date();
            d.setTime(d.getTime() + (Expiration * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
            var expires = "expires=" + d.toGMTString();
            
            document.cookie = Name + "=" + Value + "; " + expires + ";" + "path=/";
        }

        function SlideEmailPopup(Panel, Position, Speed) {
            Speed = (Speed === undefined) ? "fast" : Speed;
            $(Panel).animate({ right: Position }, Speed);
            if (Position == 0) {
                $(Panel).addClass('OpenDiv');
            }
            else {
                $(Panel).removeClass('OpenDiv');
            }
        }

        function ResizePopUp(RunAnyways) {
            var EmailPanel = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_uxEmailPopup_EmailPanel");

            if (parseInt(EmailPanel.style.right) &lt; 0 || RunAnyways) {
                EmailPanel.style.right = "-" + EmailPanel.offsetWidth + "px";
            }
        }

        window.onresize = function () {
            ResizePopUp(false);
        };
      </script>

        function GetCookie(name, key) {

                name = name.trim();
                // Check Cookies
                var cookies = document.cookie.split(';');
                for (var i = 0; i &lt; cookies.length; i++) {
                    var cookie = cookies[i].trim();
                    if (cookie.toLowerCase().indexOf(name.toLowerCase()) == 0) {
                        // Grab Cookie Value
                        value = cookie.substring(name.length + 1, cookie.length);
                        break;
                    }
                }

                if (key &amp;&amp; key.trim() != '') {
                    key = key.trim();
                    // Check Embedded Keys
                    var keypairs = value.split('&amp;');
                    for (var x = 0; x &lt; keypairs.length; x++) {
                        var keypair = keypairs[x].trim();
                        if (keypair.toLowerCase().indexOf(key.toLowerCase()) == 0) {
                            // Grab Key Value
                            value = keypair.substring(key.length + 1, keypair.length);
                            break;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            return value;
        }

        function SetCookie(Name, Value, Expiration) {
            var d = new Date();
            d.setTime(d.getTime() + (Expiration * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
            var expires = "expires=" + d.toGMTString();

            document.cookie = Name + "=" + Value + "; " + expires;
        }

        function SlideChatPopup(Panel, Position, Speed) {
            Speed = (Speed === undefined) ? "fast" : Speed;
            $(Panel).animate({ bottom: Position }, Speed);
            if (Position == 0) {
                $(Panel).addClass('OpenDiv');
            }
            else {
                $(Panel).removeClass('OpenDiv');
            }
        }

        function UpdateQueryString(uri, key, value) {
            var re = new RegExp("([?&amp;])" + key + "=.*?(&amp;|$)", "i");
            var separator = uri.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? "&amp;" : "?";
            if (uri.match(re)) {
                return uri.replace(re, '$1' + key + "=" + value + '$2');
            }
            else {
                return uri + separator + key + "=" + value;
            }
        }
      </script>
